{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775"},"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":true,"beta":false}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}]}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"animated"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserTrackingMode/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse":{"title":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnusertrackingmode\/mlnusertrackingmodefollowwithcourse","abstract":[],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/setTargetCoordinate:animated:":{"role":"symbol","title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoo